    "rationale": "12 of 13 V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged and accepted on the basis that static compression-bending is the most conservative and clinically relevant loading mode for this submission, and that the regulatory predicate comparison does not require dynamic validation at this stage. All QoI acceptance bounds satisfied (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%). Package accepted for inclusion in 510(k) submission.",
